The default value for apps that target API level 27 or lower is "true". Apps that target API level 28 or higher default to "false". The key reason for avoiding cleartext traffic is the lack of confidentiality, authenticity, and protections against tampering; a network attacker can eavesdrop on transmitted data and also modify it without being detected.

playstore_details.title: Richamster - Cryptocurrency trading mobile app
playstore_details.description:
Richamster is an application for Richamster.com, and was inspired by the work of the Karbo community.

RicHamster is one of the most trusted and secure cryptocurrency exchanges in Ukraine and across the globe,  providing multilingual support we give our users a comfortable environment. It is the fastest way to buy cryptocurrencies without the involvement of any intermediary, directly through your bank account in a matter of seconds. 

We are a group of crypto enthusiasts and believe in total participation hence we give every individual a chance to become a part of our project by purchasing some stakes of our organisation. These stakes defines the role of the individual and even ables him to decide the future of the organisation by giving the investors- the right of vote and to keep their opinions on the table, with this futuristic approach we have successfully become one of the fastest growing exchanges with high level of liquidity.

Features of the mobile application:
 
Low Trading fee:
We understand the user's annoyance to high trading fees hence we impose a minimal trading fee. 

Trade (buy/sell):
Buy and sell cryptocurrencies in a click with the ultimate security of richamster

Deposit & withdraw:
Deposit as well as withdraw coins from the application itself in much more convenient manner using QR codes and other cutting edge tech.

Order history:
View all the complete and pending orders in the android application itself, also cancel orders from the app with a click.

Charts:
Specially for trading enthusiasts we provide live chart of all currencies aiding the user to analyse the trends and plan their moves accordingly.

Security:
The application comes with a fingerprint and passcode authentication security so as to prevent unauthorized access.

Multi-lingual:
We Support several languages so as to give the users the comforting feel they deserve.

24x7 Support:
Contact us from the android application or through our website Richamster.com , alternatively you can also follow us at
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/richamstercom
Telegram: https://t.me/richamster_chat

For QnA and FAQs visit : https://richamster.com/faq/
